I have yet to write a README. Some better documentation will come soon.

However, the very basic usage that converts Ordnance Survey eastings and northings into latitudes/longitudes is something like:

require 'os-opendata-utils'
OsOpendataUtils::GridReference.new(357235,  171985).to_lat_lng

CREDITS:

Ruby implementation by Neil Smith - http://github.com/smugx
Original PHP implementation of Latitude/Longitude conversion by Pezholio - http://github.com/pezholio/UK-Postcodes
